 schools career history cofounder   current permian investment partners lp permian investment partners manages the permian master fund which employs a longshort special situations investment strategy the fund invests in small and midcap companies that are located mainly in western europe permian investment invests across all sectors with the exception of the financial and insurance sectors analyst prior   brahman capital corp brahman capital corp serves as the investment manager of various longshort and longonly private investment funds the firm seeks to construct portfolios in which performance is determined by stock selection rather than overall market direction each longshort fund seeks to generate returns through individual stock selection on both its long and short holdings brahmans longshort strategy is a fundamental strategy that focuses primarily on disciplined free cash flow value investing with a strong emphasis on the quality of company management each fund’s long and short positions primarily consist of equity andor equityrelated securities of us or nonus corporations partnerships or other entities that brahman believes to be undervalued or overvalued respectively each fund’s investments generally include special situations involving the securities and other financial instruments of issuers engaged in extraordinary corporate events such as ceo changes spinoffs takeover attempts mergers tender offers postbankruptcy reorganizations liquidations lbos stock repurchase programs and other forms of corporate restructurings brahmins longonly funds focus primarily on long positions in equity or equityrelated securities of us and nonus companies they believe to be undervalued the funds generally include all of the long positions in the longshort funds other than market hedges analyst    merrill lynch  co inc merrill lynch is one of the world’s premier providers of wealth management securities trading and sales corporate finance and investment banking services more than  professionals in  countries combine local market expertise with merrill lynch’s substantial global product resources technology and capital other affiliations scott michael hendrickson is affiliated with permian investment partners lp brahman capital corp merrill lynch  co inc youve reached your  free profiles limit this month upgrade to relsci pro today to enjoy unlimited article views and much more start my free trial ➤ still not convinced check out our full listing of features here are you a relsci pro subscriber login to relsci pro  ➤ not a pro subscriber log in here to manage your alerts keep me signed in login  ➤ forgot your password i have read the lexisnexis terms  conditions sign me up  ➤ permian investment partners lp in new york ny   chamberofcommercecom  sign up sign in contact us   search   near   home » new york » new york » specialized insurance » permian investment partners lp permian investment partners lp  reviews  stars  based on  reviews  e th st fl  new york new york        print  save  directions about permian investment partners lp is located at the address  e th st fl  in new york new york  they can be contacted via phone at   for pricing hours and directions permian investment partners lp has an annual sales volume of m –  for more information contact cara goldenberg chief executive officerpermian investment partners lp provides banking family wealth planning estimates to its customers for maps and directions to permian investment partners lp view the map to the right for reviews of permian investment partners lp see below business features products group policies  profit sharing plans  combination policies  treasury bonds  bonds  securities  loans  iras  agency bonds  industrial policies services rollovers  business banking  estimates  consultations  family wealth planning  retirement services  financial services  insurance  long term planning  banking   information contact information phone   additional information employee size  to